This product includes software developed by the TurboPress authors.

The quantization pipeline builds on the primitives introduced in TurboQuant
(arXiv:2504.19874): a seeded randomized orthogonal transform, an MSE-optimal
scalar quantizer, and a Quantized-JL residual sketch. TurboPress adds
trellis-coded quantization with data-free trellis-optimized codebooks,
rotation-aware ("quarter-power") activation equilibration, GPTQ/LDLQ error
feedback, and per-layer bit allocation, together with a measurement harness
that reports KL, top-1 agreement, and perplexity against the full-precision
model.

